<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
<head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8'>
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge'>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'>
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-iYQeCzEYFbKjA/T2uDLTpkwGzCiq6soy8tYaI1GyVh/UjpbCx/TYkiZhlZB6+fzT" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        #todoEmail{
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        #todoEmail p{
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #000;
        }
        h1{
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #3742fa;
        }
        h2{
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #3742fa;
        }
        span{
            font-weight: 700;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id='todoEmail' class="container">
        <h1>Todo App</h1>
        <h2>Verification Email</h2>
        
        <p>Hi {{name}}</p>
        <p class="greeting-p">
            We are glad to have you in our app, we hope that this app helps you in organizing your <span>todos</span>
            and achieving your <span>goals</span>.
        </p>
        <p class="verification-p">
            In order to be able to use all features of our app, you must be verified first, 
            so please go to <a href="{{link}}">this Link</a> to be verified.
        </p>
        <p>Thanks <br> Todos App Team</p>
        
    </div>    
</body>
</html>